{"tid":237255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【霧霾毒港】5月現嚴重污染情況罕見 專家：不宜室外工作","createTime":"2017-05-10T09:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T09:13:54.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c544f07ae79a9e064661e8feed06d3d024c8feb","tid":237255,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:10:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>【霧霾毒港】5月現嚴重污染情況罕見 專家：不宜室外工作</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170510/large/1494406895_ab28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170510%2Flarge%2F1494406895_ab28.jpg&h=891f17d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環保署今在各區的監測站，均錄得空氣質素健康風險指數由甚高至嚴重。從天文台在港九新界所拍攝的錄像顯示，無論是市區或是戶外，濃霧在天空蓋上灰濛濛一片，從太平山遠眺維港時，甚至一度未能看到對岸建築物。<br />\n<br />\n健康空氣行動社區關係經理龍子維指出，5月份就出現如此嚴重的空氣污染情況較罕見。他查找過粵港澳空氣質素發佈平台資料，指最高數值地區都在香港境內，PM2.5（微細懸浮粒子）超過每立方米200微克，廣東省如江門、廣州一帶都只有每立方米70至80微克左右，相信本港空氣污染與氣象條件有關。<br />\n<br />\n龍子維解釋，本港現時正吹微弱南風、東風，令本地車輛等廢氣排放較易積聚，加上夏天日照陽光令PM2.5更易形成，令污染物濃度急升。他形容現時本港空氣污染水平「實在太高」，出現如此污染度是「一次都唔理想」。他提醒市民不宜室外工作，尤其在車多地區。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170510/56675647\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170510%2F56675647&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmeuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=1007bf0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170510%2F56675647&h=b1681605\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170510/56675647</a>"},{"pid":"b1f531641943e435cbcff2092c090564f3733ca0","tid":237255,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"肯定係腥港污染支那啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">曲</span></span>"},{"pid":"6b6584638003aed9ab259228dfdd84f20765bd67","tid":237255,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e241eacb1983c526099b52d8063b3cd71dc89e","tid":237255,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}